## Non-goals / deferred

- Destructive container operations (restart, kill, exec with arbitrary
  commands) are NOT introduced here. Those remain behind `plan_action` +
  the execute agent's existing Swarm tools.
- Network layer repair tools (iptables manipulation, overlay rebuild) are
  separate — candidate for v2.35+ and require careful blast_radius design.
- Cross-container probe orchestration (probe between N:M pairs automatically)
  is a potential v2.35 composite built on these primitives.


